
This user story starts with Valentina. Valentina is a 32 year old reporter for a local newspaper. 
She has a constantly changing schedule, has to travel around the Greater Boston Area frequently, 
and always needs to be up to date with the latest news. To make sure she is where she needs to be on time, 
she has linked her Google Calendar account to the Daily Briefing to know what she has coming up next. 
Valentina also keeps up to date with Uber/Lyft price estimates to get to these locations, as well as 
public transportation options. She also is breifed with current news updates from her favorite sources, 
so she always stays current in an ever changing news environment. 